{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/fe/2020/02/21/Windows安装flutter开发环境.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"fe417b5c-fb51-57c5-a786-bbd0847103aa","excerpt":"Windows 安装 flutter 开发环境 从 chocolatey 可以直接安装 flutter。 运行成功后可以运行检查环境是否完备，比如我会有报错，可以运行以下命令检查详情。 发现 SDK 管理的问题，进而发现要把 JDK 降级到 8.0，好在有 chocolatey，很快就解决了。 然后修改.bashrc…","html":"<h1>Windows 安装 flutter 开发环境</h1>\n<p>从 chocolatey 可以直接安装 flutter。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> choco <span class=\"token function\">install</span> flutter</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>运行成功后可以运行<code class=\"language-text\">flutter doctor</code>检查环境是否完备，比如我会有<code class=\"language-text\">X Android license status unknown.</code>报错，可以运行以下命令检查详情。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\">flutter doctor --android-licenses</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>发现 SDK 管理的问题，进而发现要把 JDK 降级到 8.0，好在有 chocolatey，很快就解决了。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> choco <span class=\"token function\">install</span> ojdkbuild8</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>然后修改.bashrc 设置代理</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">HTTP_PROXY</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">127.0</span>.0.1:1080\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">HTTPS_PROXY</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">127.0</span>.0.1:1080\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">NO_PROXY</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">127.0</span>.0.1,localhost</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>打开 VScode，安装 flutter，打开命令面板输入<code class=\"language-text\">flutter new</code>，就可以创建工程了（然后下载了巨多文件，感觉如果写个 hello world 都要加载这么多文件真是比较坑）。</p>\n<p>打开模拟器，在 VSCode 里面按 F5 就能实时 debug 了。</p>","frontmatter":{"category":"fe"},"fields":{"slug":"/fe/2020/02/21/Windows安装flutter开发环境.html","date":"February 21, 2020","title":"Windows安装flutter开发环境"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/fe/2020/02/21/Windows安装flutter开发环境.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/movie/2020/02/17/电影补档计划：时空恋旅人.html","title":"电影补档计划：时空恋旅人"},"frontmatter":{"category":"movie"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/fe/2020/02/22/我也谈谈hoisting.html","title":"我也谈谈hoisting"},"frontmatter":{"category":"fe"}}}}}